Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coby-Meppo's Resolve!\NVice-Admiral Garp's Parental Affection"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A million Little Garden residents\Nare out to greet Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls' high-pitched cheers...\NKisses being blown all over the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I'm so popular\Nthat it's almost a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall in love with me, Mademoiselle.\NIt's not my fault if you get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid? Hey, I heard that, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Keep it down, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. So...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, so it's like I was just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any islands, but it's easy\Nto hit reefs due to the elevated coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. That was helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow, it smells good.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting. This is\Ntoday's dessert, Tarte aux Poires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon appetit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Hmm? Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I asked him to go draw water earlier.\NI want to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's at the water-drawing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he's been quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Luffy! Why'd you have to break it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to\Ndraw the water faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy... The belt's\Nbeen burned and broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wonder how that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of your ridiculous strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we have to get\Nmaterials from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I probably\Nshouldn't ask him to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, could you get water from the\Nother water-drawing machine for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nami! Have you ever\Nconsidered doing it yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, show a little more remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sorry. But there's another\None, so what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san, look.\N--I'm sorry. But there's another\None, so what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san, look.\N--Saying something like that\Nshows you're not sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, the newspaper courier.\N--Shut up! I can't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I can't believe they deliver\Nthe morning paper at snack time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be helped since we're\Ntraveling in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should feel lucky that\Nwe can still get news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something catch your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ah, no, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Zoro, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is just\Na picture of the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:05:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but the guy in this\Npicture isn't just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Hey, it's Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby...? That friend you were\Ntalking about the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! So what does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it say? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Vice-Admiral Garp's warship has\Narrived at Navy Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The picture was taken right after\Nthey crossed over Reverse Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as expected, Vice-Admiral\NGarp had a relaxed, imposing look;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,however, there were some young\Nmarines whose faces froze with fear."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... So Coby has\Nentered the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said Navy Headquarters. Not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what people say,\Nhe's a man who'll be a Navy mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he want to become a mayor?\NOfficer! A Navy officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So he's trying hard, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:06:04.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,000 push-ups! Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope-crossing, 100 round trips!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run 200 laps!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can't finish within 1 hour\Nwill be penalized with another 100 laps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop until you faint!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Navy Headquarters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"23"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, they can't see us here.\NPlease rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Coby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was too early\Nfor us to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it earlier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way we are right now,\Nwe won't make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a proper order for doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should try again after\Nwe've at least trained ourselves more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! That's right. Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're missing,\Nno one will care...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you thinking, Helmeppo-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said\Nyou'd surpass your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I did... but if I do\Nall those things, I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you be happy\Nif that's the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've decided\Nto become like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've decided\Nto become like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to be\NKing of the Pirates, so if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can die fighting for that,\Nyou should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting... That's going a bit far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against yourself!\NSo please don't ever say you'll run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure aren't going to\Nbring disgrace on me, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can be easily replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna run away,\Nhurry up and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! We won't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far fully\Nprepared to die if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us any orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll carry out anything,\NVice-Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry out anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've come fully prepared to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely said that, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop slacking off here\Nand get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could continue watching them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Navy Headquarters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As people say,\NVice-Admiral Garp seems quite eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's higher up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then those two must be promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!\NStupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let them go\Nwithout saying anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!\NStupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... wanted to play with them more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to them more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was learning how to cook so that\NI could make them a tasty lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even say... good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they leave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, I'm sorry! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika, that's enough. Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. They'll surely come back...\Nafter becoming fine officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can we really become marines\Nby doing things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be that old\Ndog's hobby, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. A hobby called\N"the retired geezer's torment of youths."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's possible\Nsince he seems crafty and eccentric?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:11:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, birds!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old geezer sure is\Nquick to resort to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Vice-Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he's called "Garp the Fist"\Nand quite feared by everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder his fist was\Nheavier than Alvida's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the point!\NStop with the pointless chatter already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially while we're working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get me in trouble, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so coldhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our joint responsibility.\NWe're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that only when\Nit's convenient for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please work more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go back to how I used to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use saying\Nsomething like that now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...although it's a different story\Nif we became a Navy officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't run away, nor can we slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, there's only one\Nway to go back to how I used to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be becoming important\Nquickly, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't I think"? There's no\Nway things can be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to work hard\Nand steadily with patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna take an easy way? That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing only chores and continuing to\Nwait around won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think I'll strengthen my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?\NYou know that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We work so hard during the day\Nthat we're physically a wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become important and go\Nback to how I used to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surpass my dad, too.\NI've decided just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... There's no way\Nthat your body can keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Impossible!\NImpossible! Definitely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've decided\Nto become that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you can die fighting for that,\Nyou should be happy! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've... already decided.\NWell, I don't wanna die, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no turning back.\NI'll go as far as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Coby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What is it, Coby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known better...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carelessly said wimpy\Nthings like I used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. The issue isn't\Nif we can do it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we have the will to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided just now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your motive is a little impure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go along with your spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll compete\Nand see who drops first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I want!\NI'm telling you now that I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Say whatever you want!\NSee you later. I'm going ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That's not nice to go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? We're not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time\Nto be buddy-buddy with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?\NThat's not what you said earlier at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! One, two! One...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Straw Hat Luffy,\Nthe 30 million-Berry bounty head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to capture a vicious,\Ndirty pirate like him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as possible\Nand put him to execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san is wanted for bounty...\NSomething is wrong, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! A pirate is a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's caught,\Nhe's set to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not that easy\Nto accept it, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san and I are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! No marine has\Na pirate for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll get fired from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say such a thing anywhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You swear? Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V-V-Vice-Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You guys were talking\Nabout something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear it, too.\NSo who's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two're friends\Nwith that Straw Hat Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if Helmeppo-san is, but I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:17:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that we are friends\Neven if we're apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're aware of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't keep people\Nlike that in the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But fortunately,\NI'm the only one who knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna be a marine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm Luffy-san's friend,\Nbut Helmeppo-san has nothing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do! That's why we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! He isn't someone\Nwho'd listen to that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's joint responsibility.\NJoint responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Coby?!\NDon't you wanna be one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, stop grumbling\Nand bring it on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna die that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to be a marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die fighting for it, I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way we'd give it up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man who will become a Navy officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:19:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Navy officer, huh? That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People here have been calling\Nme eccentric for quite a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and especially this time,\Nthey said all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I brought you here, I have to\Ntrain you so that you'll be very useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested you two to see\Nwhat you are really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we're really like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it may appear that you've been\Ntrying hard strengthening your bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might\Nstill be weak mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I tested you to see if you're\Nworking with firm determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the verdict?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll acknowledge your determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've still got a long way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to weakness,\Nyou guys take the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have an intense\Nspecial training every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll overlook your friend situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cherish that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir! Thank you very much,\NVice-Admiral Garp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, gentle song
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it there for us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a wave washed away\Nthat little sand castle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked up at the passing\Nclouds with a sad smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find the world is full of enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold you in my arms forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Little Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:22:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "little" about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an undiscovered land.\NIt's a thick jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope there's a BBQ restaurant in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if there'd be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't normal!\NThis is definitely not normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided that we're not gonna go\Nashore on this island... Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell adventure in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Ancient Island!\NThe Shadow Hiding in Little Garden!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
